│ POINTS & FLAGS** ([replai.py](replai.py))\n\nThree main commands:\n\n- **` │
│ play`**: Terminal playback\n  - `--show-reasoning`: Display reasoning bloc │
│ ks\n  - `--speed FACTOR`: Playback multiplier (default: 1.0)\n  - `--tool- │
│ visibility {full|minimal|hidden}`: Controls noisy tool display\n\n- **`ser │
│ ve`**: Browser viewer\n  - `--output PATH`: Save HTML to file\n  - `--http │
│ `: Use localhost server (default: direct HTML file)\n  - `--port PORT`: HT │
│ TP port (default: 8000)\n\n- **`html`**: Export static HTML\n  - `--output │
│  PATH`: Write to file (default: stdout)\n  - `--open`: Open in browser\n\n │
│ ---\n\n### **2. DATA MODEL: ATIF v1.5 JSON FORMAT** ([replay_core.py](repl │
│ ay_core.py))\n\n**Root structure:**\n```json\n{\n  \"schema_version\": \"1 │
│ .5\",\n  \"session_id\": \"string\",\n  \"agent\": { \"name\": \"string\"  │
│ },\n  \"steps\": [...]\n}\n```\n\n**Step structure:**\n```json\n{\n  \"ste │
│ p_id\": 1,\n  \"timestamp\": \"ISO8601Z\",\n  \"message\": { \"role\": \"u │
│ ser|agent|system|tool\", \"content\": \"string\" },\n  \"tool_calls\": [\n │
│     { \"id\": \"string\", \"name\": \"string\", \"arguments\": {} }\n  ],\ │
│ n  \"observation\": {\n    \"results\": [\n      { \"source_call_id\": \"s │
│ tring\", \"content\": \"any\" }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"metrics\": { \"prompt_to │
│ kens\": 0, \"completion_tokens\": 0, ... },\n  \"reasoning_content\": \"st │
│ ring\"\n}\n```\n\n**Normalized Events** (internal representation):\n- `Eve │
│ nt` dataclass: `kind` (message|reasoning|tool_call|tool_result|metrics), ` │
│ step_id`, `ts`, `role`, `title`, `body`, `ref`\n\n---\n\n### **3. HOW buil │
│ d_html IS CALLED** ([browser_view.py](browser_view.py))\n\n```python\ndef  │
│ build_html(doc: Optional[dict], events: List[Event]) -> str:\n    # Conver │
│ ts doc + events to static HTML\n    # Expected inputs:\n    # - doc: Full  │
│ ATIF document or None\n    # - events: Normalized event list from normaliz │
│ e()\n    \n    context = {\n        \"page_title\": doc.get(\"session_id\" │
│ ) if doc else \"open local trajectory\",\n        \"browser_css\": BROWSER │
│ _CSS,  # From browser_assets.py\n        \"browser_js\": BROWSER_JS,    #  │
│ From browser_assets.py\n        \"initial_events_json\": _js_safe_json([da │
│ taclasses.asdict(ev) for ev in events]),\n        \"initial_raw_doc_json\" │
│ : _js_safe_json(doc),\n    }\n    return _render_template(context)\n```\n\ │
│ n**Flow:**\n1. Load file → validate → normalize → build_html\n2. Jinja2 re │
│ nders [browser_template.html.j2](browser_template.html.j2)\n3. Template in │
│ jects CSS, JS, and data (JSON) at script time\n\n---\n\n### **4. COPILOT J │
│ SONL IMPORT** ([replay_core.py](replay_core.py))\n\n**Input format** (Copi │
│ lot main.jsonl):\n```jsonl\n{\"type\":\"user_message\",\"ts\":1234567,\"at │
│ trs\":{\"content\":\"...\"}}\n{\"type\":\"agent_response\",\"ts\":1234568, │
│ \"attrs\":{\"response\":\"[...]\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"ts\":123456 │
