│ l_1\"}}\n{\"type\":\"child_session_ref\",\"attrs\":{\"childLogFile\":\"chi │
│ ld.jsonl\"}}\n```\n\n**Processing:**\n- Parses JSONL line-by-line\n- Group │
│ s events by step (user/agent pairs)\n- Attaches tool calls & results to mo │
