│ 5 doc with proper validation\n\n---\n\n### **5. BROWSER UI & CONSUMPTION** │
│  ([browser_app.js](browser_app.js) & [browser_template.html.j2](browser_te │
│ mplate.html.j2))\n\n**Data flow:**\n1. Template injects `INITIAL_EVENTS` a │
│ nd `INITIAL_RAW_DOC` as globals\n2. JavaScript normalizes doc → events\n3. │
│  Renders conversation chain with steps grouped by step_id\n\n**Key UI feat │
│ ures:**\n- **Collapse/expand**: Toggle steps with keyboard shortcut `f`\n- │
│  **Navigation**: Arrow keys or `j/k`, `Home/End`\n- **Filter chain**: Text │
